Mook omits from qnorum to inuenies, and has a few slight alterations of punctuation and spelling. He gives this book among those without date, No. 245, but in a note undet· date 1569 identifies it with one of a similar title mentioned by Gesner and concludes that the present volume was really printed in 1568.
